{"tid":316873,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"第一屆世紀帝國三香港區夏季賽","createTime":"2017-07-11T05:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T04:59:24.000Z","uid":121493,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ac64f4f11572fbf8981f140067c901a47add4c3d","tid":316873,"uid":121493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:16:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一屆Aoe3巴打夏季賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>賽制：</strong> <br />\n<br />\n1.淘汰型式  bo1 一場過<br />\n2.決賽階段  bo3 三盤兩勝，有季軍爭奪戰，同樣bo3<br />\n3.雙方預先私下同裁判講定用邊一個國，揀好左唔可以臨尾轉，避免後選剋制問題<br />\n但係可以係雙方同意下進行鏡像對戰 (雙方選同一個國)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>比賽版本：</strong> <br />\nAoe3 亞洲王朝 ESOC patch (外國比賽專用版本)<br />\n<a href=\"http://eso-community.net/esoc-patch.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feso-community.net%2Fesoc-patch.php&d=vG6ne3CU2QwHKE9ve8qjYbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=006cea1c\" target=\"_blank\">http://eso-community.net/esoc-patch.php</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>地圖：</strong> ESOC 隨機地圖 (比賽專用圖之中隨機抽選)<br />\n<strong>比賽server：</strong>官方伺服器ESO <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">(有AC可以借比無正版又想參與既巴打)</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">Facebook</span></strong>: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkgol\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkgol&d=vG6ne3CU2QwHKE9ve8qjYbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=0bc761a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkgol</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">Telegram</span></strong>: <a href=\"https://telegram.me/joinchat/CI9Fzj9FGObEDXQmhk8nDQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.me%2Fjoinchat%2FCI9Fzj9FGObEDXQmhk8nDQ&d=vG6ne3CU2QwHKE9ve8qjYbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=bef14508\" target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.me/joinchat/CI9Fzj9FGObEDXQmhk8nDQ</a><br />\n裁判+解說員+錄製直播：<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/u_ya\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fu_ya&d=vG6ne3CU2QwHKE9ve8qjYbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8657f06b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/u_ya</a><br />\n<br />\n暫時未有獎品，贏左今次比賽既冠軍可以係下一次做衛冕者，亞季軍做種子<br />\n如果反應熱烈之後可能會有Steam卡 / google play卡做獎品<br />\n<br />\n報名：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe-nHgivXid-pkvc5PYMrPSFQEFppiF-2tvEVNJgmqxOaXOYQ/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSe-nHgivXid-pkvc5PYMrPSFQEFppiF-2tvEVNJgmqxOaXOYQ%2Fviewform&d=vG6ne3CU2QwHKE9ve8qjYbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=d8a2746b\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe-nHgivXid-pkvc5PYMrPSFQEFppiF-2tvEVNJgmqxOaXOYQ/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n名額：目前預16人，可以再加</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e7f45528a39bb36513ed40175ab6e71245e6f8b1","tid":316873,"uid":50655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T07:28:23.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"04147a75e8ad2828df7595de89359d1278ab0c28","tid":316873,"uid":18333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T08:09:05.000Z","msg":"冇玩第3集, 支持!"},{"pid":"14ae12f3ce5d35eed71dbbd573454f99cde6c4ee","tid":316873,"uid":121493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T10:11:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇玩第3集, 支持!</blockquote><br />\n依家開始學都黎得切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9270862c96268bbf65f4177718a6573f34be68b4","tid":316873,"uid":46085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:59:34.000Z","msg":"support <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079c1569a45c1de1318